"Viber dispatcher to send private message\n"
"\n"
"#### Get API keys\n"
"\n"
"* Register at [[https://partners.viber.com/about]]\n"
"* Click on [Create Bot Account](https://partners.viber.com/account/create-"
"bot-account)\n"
"* Copy the token and paste it here"
